Units and Entities have Templates\par
Units and Entities can have Multiple Templates? (For example, attaching a radar to multiple units or structures)\par
Templates can have Templates? (multiple parent logic, amkes sure no conflict)\par
Templates never appear in-game, only Units/Entities\par
You attach as many Templates you want to the single Faction Unit/Entity, then build said Unit\par
\par
So there is a:\par
Soldier Template\par
Infantry Template\par
Rifle Template\par
Faction 1 Unit\par
\par
Health Template\par
Health Regen Template\par
\par
The Infantry Template is attached to the Soldier Template\par
The Rifle Template is attached to the Soldier Template\par
So 2 Templates are attached to the Soldier Template\par
The Soldier Template is attached to the Faction 1 Unit\par
Faction 1 Unit is built, and it shows up as a Faction 1 Soldier Unit\par
