When to use templates, and when to use code?\par
If at any time that any detection is necessary for a category to collate units in a list, and also requires specific variables that apply to more than just one unit, then use a template.\par
For example, if I ever need a detection list of all units with veterancy, and also veterancy has a set of specific variables, then that is a template.\par
\par
So these wouldn't be full templates, then. More like a state machine of sorts.\par
For multiple templates, make a map or list or something. (DONE)\par
