There are also:\par
Health Template\par
Health Regen Template (requires Health Template)\par
\par
Health Template is attached to Soldier at Create Event\par
Soldier is wounded\par
Medic targets those with Health Templates\par
Well, a medic gives a regeneration shot to the Soldier as it has a Health Template\par
The regeneration shot attaches a Health Regen Template on the Soldier\par
\par
If the Soldier does not have Health Template\par
If for some reason the regeneration shot hits the Soldier and succeeds\par
The regeneration shot will first apply the Health Template before applying the Health Regen Template\par
